{"tid":1954093,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港共 : 呼籲用戶留意Zoom個人資料保安情況","createTime":"2020-04-01T14:31:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T14:39:37.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0c086ff079c7bcae07b21e5359bda97837948d67","tid":1954093,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:31:49.000Z","msg":"私隱專員公署籲用戶留意Zoom個人資料保安情況<br />\n01.04.2020 22:22<br />\n私隱專員公署指，留意到有報道指網上會議程式「Zoom」轉移用戶資料，呼籲用戶關注個人資料保安情況。公署指，Zoom被指曾將使用iOS手機應用程式用戶的資料，轉移至Facebook後，表示已經更新應用程式，取消資料轉移功能。私隱專員建議，使用者如決定繼續使用程式，應將手機應用程式更新到最新版本，以專為Zoom建立的帳戶登入，為會議設置密碼，及留意帳戶任何異常活動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1278153&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1278153%26csid%3D261_341&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUpuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=dd52522d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1278153&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"e81ae52148cd3472d828a6582f051f032f5d7591","tid":1954093,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:32:44.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>想要抗爭型立法會議員？投票啦！<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n畀2020年立法會選舉候選人嘅「五大訴求」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1944136\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1944136</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dfb7bf9d14b45224b7cf26c25ebd56c55ca93670","tid":1954093,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:39:37.000Z","msg":"[理論]如何借藍絲五毛去擴大我哋嘅勢力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1954032\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1954032</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}